Feature: Login
  Given on the login page
  When input your username
  When input your password
  And click login button
  Then directed to home page of saucedemo.com


Feature: Sort item products
  Given Homepage Catalog of Swag Labs Products
  When click filter dropdown
  And click filter Price (low to High)
  Then filter product by the lowest price
  When click filter dropdown
  And click filter Price (High to High)
  Then filter product by the lowest price
  When click filter dropdown
  And click filter Name (A to Z)
  Then filter product by the lowest price
  When click filter dropdown
  And click filter Name (Z to A)
  Then filter product by the lowest price


Feature: Add Item to Cart
  Given Homepage Catalog of Swag Labs Products
  When click add to cart button
  And item added to cart and adding a number of total item
  When add another item to add to cart
  When click cart icon to proceed the transactions


Feature: Remove choosen product
  Given Homepage Catalog of Swag Labs Products
  When item are checked or added to cart
  Click remove button to remove added item on cart
  Then remove the item and empty the cart


Feature: Checkout the item on cart
  Given Cart item detail, price and description
  When click checkout button
  Then direct to checkout personal information page


Feature: Remove cart product item
  Given Cart item detail, price and description
  Click remove button to remove added item on cart
  Then remove the item and empty the cart


Feature: Checkout Personal Information with empty infomation
  Given Personal Information page
  When keep empty first name, last name or/and postal code
  When click continue button
  Then shows error information cannot be empty


Feature: Checkout Personal Information
  Given Personal Information page
  When input your first name
  And input your last name
  And input your ZIP / Postal Code must be a number
  Then Click continue button


Feature: Checkout Overview
  Given Checkout Overview detail information
  When check Payment Information, Shipping Information
  And Item Total and total tax
  And Total price include tax
  When Click finish button
  Then direct to complete the transaction popup information
